\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{1000 \sqrt n}
\frac{1}{1000}\sum_{n=1}^{N}\frac{1}{\sqrt n}\gt\frac{1}{1000}\sum_{n=1}^{N}\frac{1}{n}\to\infty\ \ (N\to\infty).
 \sum_1^{N^2} \frac{1}{\sqrt{n}} > 1+\frac{1}{2} + \frac{1}{3} + \dots + \frac{1}{N} 
n!\lt n^n
\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{1}{\sqrt k}\gt n\sqrt[n]{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n!}}}\gt\frac{n}{\sqrt[2n]{n!}}\gt\frac{n}{\sqrt n}=\sqrt n.
 \begin{align} \sum_{k=1}^n\frac1{1000\sqrt{k}} &\ge\frac1{500}\sum_{k=1}^n\frac1{\sqrt{k+1}+\sqrt{k}}\\ &=\frac1{500}\sum_{k=1}^n(\sqrt{k+1}-\sqrt{k})\\[4pt] &=\frac{\sqrt{n+1}-1}{500} \end{align} 
